I went to Dr Sudarshan to get 4 dental implants on the upper and lower jaw on the right hand side. I already had 3 or 4 implants from another doctor who had done a good job. I decided to switch my doctor to Sudarshan because i had gone to him for other things and liked him. I have to say that Dr Sudarshan did an excellent job in many ways. 1. I communicated that pain management was very important to me. He was very good in handling this made sure that in a surgery like putting in implants he paid enough attention that the pain factor during surgery was minimal (remember they drill into the jawbone when this is done) 2. My previous dentist while being good was twice as expensive as Dr Sudarshan for a procedure like implants. Very happy overall. Will recommend him without qualification.
